org.apache.hawq.pxf.plugins.hbase.utilities

Class HBaseIntegerComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.filter.ByteArrayComparable
      • org.apache.hawq.pxf.plugins.hbase.utilities.HBaseIntegerComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<byte[]>

    public class HBaseIntegerComparator
extends org.apache.hadoop.hbase.filter.ByteArrayComparable
    This is a Filter comparator for HBase It is external to PXF HBase code.

    To use with HBase it must reside in the classpath of every region server.

    It converts a value into Long before comparing. The filter is good for any integer numeric comparison i.e. integer, bigint, smallint.

    according to HBase 0.96 requirements, this must serialized using Protocol Buffers (toByteArray() and parseFrom(byte[]) methods).

    A reference can be found in SubstringComparator.
